title: S2: MF DOOM, Part 6 - Apartment 6G
description:
As ZEV LOVE X deals with the loss of his brother DJ Subroc and the loss of his recording contract with Elektra, ZEV LOVE X begins his migration from Long Beach to Harlem.  He begins to make a new family (The CM Fam) led by Kurious Jorge, Kadi, and the men who held him down creatively and emotionally in Apartment 6G.   The importance of the artistry and camaraderie of those men and woman helped formulate his next move.
